---
// Standing CTA at the end of every SMP blog post.
// Edit copy here in one place to update across the whole blog.
// Points to /contact/ — Kevin's free consultation call request page.
---

<aside class="my-12 px-6 py-10 lg:px-10 lg:py-12 rounded-2xl text-center" style="background-color: var(--color-red-wash); border: 1px solid #f4d4cf;">
	<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" style="color: var(--color-red-deep); font-family: var(--font-sans);">
		Free Consultation
	</p>
	<p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-light leading-tight max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-ink);">
		Ready to talk through your book or platform?
	</p>
	<p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-base lg:text-lg leading-relaxed" style="font-family: var(--font-sans); color: var(--color-ink-muted);">
		If you&rsquo;re a Kingdom author or ministry weighing what comes next &mdash; publishing, marketing, audience growth &mdash; we&rsquo;d be glad to listen. Schedule a free consultation call. No pitch, no pressure.
	</p>
	<a
		href="/contact/"
		class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-7 px-7 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold no-underline transition-opacity hover:opacity-90"
		style="background-color: var(--color-red); color: #ffffff; font-family: var(--font-sans);"
	>
		Schedule a Free Call
		<span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
	</a>
</aside>
